---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Educational Programs" description="Discover our play-based, child-led kindergarten programs for 3 and 4-year-olds in Ubud, Bali.">
    <!-- Hero Header -->
    <section class="bg-sunny-blue/10 py-24 px-6 md:px-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 bg-sunny-yellow/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-sunny-green/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
            <span class="text-sunny-blue font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4 block">Our Philosophy</span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-sunny-charcoal leading-tight">Educational Programs at <br/><span class="text-sunny-yellow">Bali Sunny Kids</span></h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                At Bali Sunny Kids, we believe childhood should be filled with wonder, laughter, and meaningful discovery.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy Intro -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    Young children learn best when they feel safe, loved, and free to explore—so every aspect of our programs is intentionally designed around <strong>play-based, child-led learning</strong> in a nurturing, nature-rich environment.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Drawing inspiration from globally respected approaches (play-based exploration with elements of Reggio Emilia-inspired creativity and inquiry), our curriculum honors each child's unique pace, interests, and personality while gently preparing them for future success.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We create small, caring groups where teachers act as guides and co-learners, observing closely to spark authentic projects and experiences. Our sunny, open classrooms and lush outdoor spaces in Bali become the <strong>"third teacher,"</strong> inviting curiosity about the island's vibrant nature, colors, sounds, and culture.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-sunny-yellow rounded-[3rem] rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform"></div>
                <img src="/images/gallery/kids-together.jpg" alt="Children playing with blocks" class="relative z-10 rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Program Cards -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sunny-cream space-y-24">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            
            <!-- 3-Year-Old Group -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-[4rem] shadow-xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-sunny-yellow/10">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/3 bg-sunny-yellow p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center text-sunny-charcoal">
                        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6 shadow-sm">🌱</div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">3-Year-Old Group</h2>
                        <p class="text-xl font-medium italic opacity-90">Nurturing Secure Foundations</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-2/3 p-12 md:p-16 space-y-10">
                        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 italic border-l-4 border-sunny-yellow pl-6">
                            This gentle introduction to group life helps little ones transition confidently from home to our warm, home-like school community.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🤝 Social & Emotional Growth</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Developing friendships, practicing sharing, naming feelings, and building empathy through group games and cozy moments together.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🎨 Creative Expression</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Open-ended art with natural pigments, clay sculpting, and music-making with Balinese-inspired instruments.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🏃 Physical Development</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Fine motor skills through puzzles and blocks; gross motor confidence with outdoor adventures and climbing in our garden.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🗣️ Language & Communication</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Bilingual exposure (English & Bahasa) through songs, rhymes, and stories about Bali's rice fields and sea.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 4-Year-Old Group -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-[4rem] shadow-xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-sunny-blue/10 mt-24">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/3 bg-sunny-blue p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center text-white">
                        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6 shadow-sm">🚀</div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">4-Year-Old Group</h2>
                        <p class="text-xl font-medium italic opacity-90">Building Confidence & School Readiness</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-2/3 p-12 md:p-16 space-y-10">
                        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 italic border-l-4 border-sunny-blue pl-6">
                            Building beautifully on the 3-year-old foundations, our 4-year-old program ignites excitement for learning while fostering independence.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🔤 Early Literacy & Numeracy</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Hands-on experiences like our "Magic Number" games, letter-sound hunts, and storytelling circles around school grounds.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">💡 Problem-Solving</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Solving real-life puzzles, conducting simple science experiments (floating/sinking), and following child-initiated inquiries.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🌟 Growing Independence</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Mastering self-help routines (tidying, serving snacks) and taking responsibility in classroom jobs that build pride.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sunny-charcoal text-xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🏝️ Environmental Awareness</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Deepening connection to Bali's ecosystem—exploring tropical plants, insects, weather patterns, and celebrating local traditions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Daily Rhythm Timeline -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-sunny-charcoal leading-tight">A Glimpse into Our <br/><span class="text-sunny-green underline decoration-sunny-yellow/40">Daily Rhythm</span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Our predictable yet flexible daily schedule creates security while allowing plenty of time for deep play, rest, and connection.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12 relative before:absolute before:inset-0 before:ml-5 before:-translate-x-px md:before:mx-auto md:before:translate-x-0 before:h-full before:w-1 before:bg-sunny-blue/10">
            
